<div><p>This is a work in progress: all item functionality is implemented and fully RESTful. Adding, editing, deleting, and such. I have additionally implemented adding notes TO items.</p>

<p>TODO: user login/logout, passwording, and admin stuff. We'll need to go over user management stuff for that, though.</p>
